Testing with Makefile
=====================
Makefile is provided to test for Unix like operating systems. See the 
Makefile for more details.


Available Testing Module For Now
================================

Error Handlers
--------------
    Testing for error_handlers module. 
    See the "tests/TestErrorHandlers.java" for more details.

Monsters
--------
    Fundamental sturture & file organization testing is provided. 
    Testing for Randomizing Monster instance initialization feature is 
    also provided. See the "tests/TestMonsters.java" for more details.
        
        
How To Test 
=========== 

The test program would comile and execute each testing file (or all), 
then delete the binary files (for cleaning). The followings are 
commands for testing on the command line shell:
    
Testing all modules
-------------------
    los/lgndofslnc/$> make

Testing error_handlers
----------------------
    los/lgndofslnc/$> make test_error_handlers

Testing monsters
----------------
    los/lgndofslnc/$> make test_monsters
